import React from 'react' import './../App.css' const Pdf = ({pdf}) => { const monthNames = [ "January", "February", "March", "April", "May", "June", "July", "August", "September", "October", "November", "December", ]; return (
{pdf.pdf_name}
{monthNames[parseInt(pdf.pdf_date.substr(4, 2)) - 1]}-{pdf.pdf_date.substr(0, 4)}
) } export default Pdf
